Package com.superduckinvaders.game

Contains the core classes required for the functionality of the game.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CompleteScreen
    Displays screen when game is completed
    DuckGame
    Class which holds all of the game varaibles
    GameScreen
    Screen for interaction with the game.
    LevelSelectScreen
    Screen which displays the different levels
    LoseScreen
    Screen that is displayed when a player loses.
    Minimap
    Contains methods needed to draw minimap
    Round
    Represents a round of the game played on one level with a single objective.
    SettingsScreen
    Screen which displays the sfx and music volumes
    StartScreen
    Shows the start screen (new game, settings, level select)
    WinScreen
    Screen for displaying when a player has won.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Minimap.minimapColors
    Each enumerable represents an object or obstacle in the game world.
